title: Info Day November
description: Information Day: November 16, 2022 | CSUF Satellite Student Union | Time: 4pm - 5pm | Parking Code: 902479

title: Field Trip to Pantages Theater: Lion King
description: The ASB is sponsoring a field trip to Pantages Theater in Hollywood. We are going to see The Lion King on March 18th, 2023. It is a Saturday trip, 8 am to 8 pm. We will have lunch (on your own) at Universal Citywalk and then see the matinee show and be home by 8. Reserve your ticket at the QR code outside the PE Room. We have 45 seats to sell. The price will be under $115 - we will have a set price once we know the cost of the bus. If you have questions, see Mr. Benslay

title: Yearbook Senior Quotes
description: Seniors, TODAY (Wednesday, November 2nd) is the last day to get your quote in the yearbook. Fill out the Remind form by then to get your words of wisdom in the yearbook. Don't have a blank space next to your name.

title: ASB Meeting
description: There is an ASB Meeting in the Choir Room on Thursday, Nov. 3rd. Come and sign in to earn spirit points for your class!

title: Speech and Debate
description: Dr. Jarocki is available after school on Wednesday, November 2nd, and Thursday, November 3rd for Debate prep before this Saturday's tournament!

title: Freshmen Vision and Hearing Screening
description: The freshmen will be having their vision and hearing screenings on November 4th, 2022 from 8:00 AM - 10:00 AM. Nothing needs to be done to prepare for this. Contact the Front Office if you have any questions.
